title: Imani Barbarin on Disability Rights, Navigating Ableism & Creating Change | ICONIC INTERVIEW
description:
Olayemi Olurin interviewed Tik Tok Star and Disability rights activist Imani Barbarin about her work fighting for disability rights, the collective benefits of accessibility and disability rights, the role social media has played in disability rights etc
